{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":3141,"text":"I grew up with my identical twin,"},{"time":6461,"text":"who was an incredibly loving brother."},{"time":9477,"text":"Now, one thing about being a twin is,"},{"time":12573,"text":"it makes you an expert\nat spotting favoritism."},{"time":16642,"text":"If his cookie was even\nslightly bigger than my cookie,"},{"time":21723,"text":"I had questions."},{"time":23099,"text":"And clearly, I wasn't starving."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26300,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":28873,"text":"When I became a psychologist,\nI began to notice favoritism"},{"time":33020,"text":"of a different kind;"},{"time":34758,"text":"and that is, how much more we value\nthe body than we do the mind."},{"time":40187,"text":"I spent nine years at university\nearning my doctorate in psychology,"},{"time":46245,"text":"and I can't tell you how many people\nlook at my business card and say,"},{"time":50523,"text":"\"Oh -- a psychologist.\nSo, not a real doctor,\""},{"time":56209,"text":"as if it should say that on my card."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58031,"text":"[Dr. Guy Winch, Just a Psychologist\n(Not a Real Doctor)]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":60840,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":62952,"text":"This favoritism we show the body\nover the mind --"},{"time":67360,"text":"I see it everywhere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69718,"text":"I recently was at a friend's house,"},{"time":71409,"text":"and their five-year-old\nwas getting ready for bed."},{"time":73955,"text":"He was standing on a stool\nby the sink, brushing his teeth,"},{"time":77584,"text":"when he slipped and scratched his leg\non the stool when he fell."},{"time":81996,"text":"He cried for a minute,\nbut then he got back up,"},{"time":84992,"text":"got back on the stool, and reached out\nfor a box of Band-Aids"},{"time":88530,"text":"to put one on his cut."},{"time":91050,"text":"Now, this kid could barely\ntie his shoelaces,"},{"time":95011,"text":"but he knew you have to cover a cut\nso it doesn't become infected,"},{"time":99462,"text":"and you have to care for your teeth\nby brushing twice a day."},{"time":103425,"text":"We all know how to maintain\nour physical health"},{"time":106369,"text":"and how to practice dental hygiene, right?"},{"time":108908,"text":"We've known it since\nwe were five years old."},{"time":112442,"text":"But what do we know about maintaining\nour psychological health?"},{"time":118070,"text":"Well, nothing."},{"time":119778,"text":"What do we teach our children\nabout emotional hygiene?"},{"time":124740,"text":"Nothing."},{"time":126767,"text":"How is it that we spend more time\ntaking care of our teeth"},{"time":131595,"text":"than we do our minds?"},{"time":134202,"text":"Why is it that our physical health\nis so much more important to us"},{"time":139036,"text":"than our psychological health?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":141393,"text":"We sustain psychological injuries\neven more often than we do physical ones,"},{"time":146807,"text":"injuries like failure\nor rejection or loneliness."},{"time":151037,"text":"And they can also get worse\nif we ignore them,"},{"time":153832,"text":"and they can impact our lives\nin dramatic ways."},{"time":157285,"text":"And yet, even though there are\nscientifically proven techniques"},{"time":161489,"text":"we could use to treat these\nkinds of psychological injuries,"},{"time":165803,"text":"we don't."},{"time":167374,"text":"It doesn't even occur to us\nthat we should."},{"time":170434,"text":"\"Oh, you're feeling depressed?\nJust shake it off; it's all in your head.\""},{"time":175190,"text":"Can you imagine saying that\nto somebody with a broken leg:"},{"time":178091,"text":"\"Oh, just walk it off;\nit's all in your leg.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":180907,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":183249,"text":"It is time we closed the gap"},{"time":186131,"text":"between our physical\nand our psychological health."},{"time":189243,"text":"It's time we made them more equal,"},{"time":192385,"text":"more like twins."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195148,"text":"Speaking of which,\nmy brother is also a psychologist."},{"time":198945,"text":"So he's not a real doctor, either."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201400,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":203708,"text":"We didn't study together, though."},{"time":205704,"text":"In fact, the hardest thing\nI've ever done in my life"},{"time":210119,"text":"is move across the Atlantic\nto New York City"},{"time":212889,"text":"to get my doctorate in psychology."},{"time":215698,"text":"We were apart then\nfor the first time in our lives,"},{"time":218685,"text":"and the separation was brutal\nfor both of us."},{"time":222295,"text":"But while he remained\namong family and friends,"},{"time":225566,"text":"I was alone in a new country."},{"time":228251,"text":"We missed each other terribly,"},{"time":229995,"text":"but international phone calls\nwere really expensive then,"},{"time":233172,"text":"and we could only afford to speak\nfor five minutes a week."},{"time":238459,"text":"When our birthday rolled around,"},{"time":240009,"text":"it was the first\nwe wouldn't be spending together."},{"time":242585,"text":"We decided to splurge,"},{"time":243938,"text":"and that week,\nwe would talk for 10 minutes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246128,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":247445,"text":"I spent the morning pacing around my room,\nwaiting for him to call --"},{"time":252154,"text":"and waiting ..."},{"time":254103,"text":"and waiting."},{"time":255817,"text":"But the phone didn't ring."},{"time":258125,"text":"Given the time difference, I assumed,"},{"time":260167,"text":"\"OK, he's out with friends,\nhe'll call later.\""},{"time":262489,"text":"There were no cell phones then."},{"time":264805,"text":"But he didn't."},{"time":267171,"text":"And I began to realize\nthat after being away for over 10 months,"},{"time":272253,"text":"he no longer missed me\nthe way I missed him."},{"time":276028,"text":"I knew he would call in the morning,"},{"time":278555,"text":"but that night was one of the saddest\nand longest nights of my life."},{"time":284717,"text":"I woke up the next morning."},{"time":286688,"text":"I glanced down at the phone,"},{"time":288359,"text":"and I realized\nI had kicked it off the hook"},{"time":291137,"text":"when pacing the day before."},{"time":294612,"text":"I stumbled out of bed,"},{"time":296287,"text":"I put the phone back on the receiver,\nand it rang a second later."},{"time":299764,"text":"And it was my brother,"},{"time":301448,"text":"and boy, was he pissed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303140,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":305368,"text":"It was the saddest and longest\nnight of his life as well."},{"time":309126,"text":"Now, I tried to explain\nwhat happened, but he said,"},{"time":311561,"text":"\"I don't understand."},{"time":312804,"text":"If you saw I wasn't calling you,"},{"time":314743,"text":"why didn't you just pick up\nthe phone and call me?\""},{"time":319057,"text":"He was right."},{"time":320841,"text":"Why didn't I call him?"},{"time":323187,"text":"I didn't have an answer then."},{"time":325608,"text":"But I do today,"},{"time":327083,"text":"and it's a simple one:"},{"time":329688,"text":"loneliness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331948,"text":"Loneliness creates a deep\npsychological wound,"},{"time":336021,"text":"one that distorts our perceptions\nand scrambles our thinking."},{"time":340228,"text":"It makes us believe that those around us\ncare much less than they actually do."},{"time":346034,"text":"It make us really afraid to reach out,"},{"time":348352,"text":"because why set yourself up\nfor rejection and heartache"},{"time":352466,"text":"when your heart is already aching\nmore than you can stand?"},{"time":356432,"text":"I was in the grips\nof real loneliness back then,"},{"time":359539,"text":"but I was surrounded by people all day,\nso it never occurred to me."},{"time":364273,"text":"But loneliness is defined\npurely subjectively."},{"time":368415,"text":"It depends solely on whether you feel\nemotionally or socially disconnected"},{"time":374203,"text":"from those around you."},{"time":375385,"text":"And I did."},{"time":377249,"text":"There is a lot of research on loneliness,\nand all of it is horrifying."},{"time":383499,"text":"Loneliness won't just make you miserable;"},{"time":386307,"text":"it will kill you."},{"time":387790,"text":"I'm not kidding."},{"time":388984,"text":"Chronic loneliness increases\nyour likelihood of an early death"},{"time":392599,"text":"by 14 percent."},{"time":394902,"text":"Fourteen percent!"},{"time":396780,"text":"Loneliness causes high blood pressure,"},{"time":399619,"text":"high cholesterol."},{"time":400808,"text":"It even suppress the functioning\nof your immune system,"},{"time":404557,"text":"making you vulnerable to all kinds\nof illnesses and diseases."},{"time":408613,"text":"In fact, scientists have concluded\nthat taken together,"},{"time":412175,"text":"chronic loneliness\nposes as significant a risk"},{"time":415855,"text":"for your long-term health and longevity"},{"time":418648,"text":"as cigarette smoking."},{"time":420464,"text":"Now, cigarette packs come with warnings\nsaying, \"This could kill you.\""},{"time":425033,"text":"But loneliness doesn't."},{"time":427405,"text":"And that's why it's so important"},{"time":429284,"text":"that we prioritize\nour psychological health,"},{"time":432371,"text":"that we practice emotional hygiene."},{"time":435525,"text":"Because you can't treat\na psychological wound"},{"time":438382,"text":"if you don't even know you're injured."},{"time":442076,"text":"Loneliness isn't the only\npsychological wound"},{"time":444944,"text":"that distorts our perceptions\nand misleads us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":448540,"text":"Failure does that as well."},{"time":451818,"text":"I once visited a day care center,"},{"time":454105,"text":"where I saw three toddlers\nplay with identical plastic toys."},{"time":459140,"text":"You had to slide the red button,\nand a cute doggie would pop out."},{"time":463817,"text":"One little girl tried pulling\nthe purple button, then pushing it,"},{"time":468412,"text":"and then she just sat back\nand looked at the box"},{"time":471230,"text":"with her lower lip trembling."},{"time":473029,"text":"The little boy next to her\nwatched this happen,"},{"time":476104,"text":"then turned to his box and burst\ninto tears without even touching it."},{"time":481141,"text":"Meanwhile, another little girl\ntried everything she could think of"},{"time":484607,"text":"until she slid the red button,"},{"time":486415,"text":"the cute doggie popped out,\nand she squealed with delight."},{"time":490421,"text":"So: three toddlers\nwith identical plastic toys,"},{"time":494233,"text":"but with very different\nreactions to failure."},{"time":497893,"text":"The first two toddlers were perfectly\ncapable of sliding a red button."},{"time":502455,"text":"The only thing that prevented\nthem from succeeding"},{"time":505590,"text":"was that their mind tricked them\ninto believing they could not."},{"time":509920,"text":"Now, adults get tricked this way\nas well, all the time."},{"time":514028,"text":"In fact, we all have a default set\nof feelings and beliefs"},{"time":519205,"text":"that gets triggered whenever\nwe encounter frustrations and setbacks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":523324,"text":"Are you aware of how\nyour mind reacts to failure?"},{"time":526783,"text":"You need to be."},{"time":528033,"text":"Because if your mind tries to convince you\nyou're incapable of something,"},{"time":532430,"text":"and you believe it,"},{"time":533963,"text":"then like those two toddlers,\nyou'll begin to feel helpless"},{"time":537261,"text":"and you'll stop trying too soon,\nor you won't even try at all."},{"time":540859,"text":"And then you'll be even more\nconvinced you can't succeed."},{"time":543967,"text":"You see, that's why so many people\nfunction below their actual potential."},{"time":548951,"text":"Because somewhere along the way,\nsometimes a single failure"},{"time":552259,"text":"convinced them that they couldn't\nsucceed, and they believed it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":556900,"text":"Once we become convinced of something,\nit's very difficult to change our mind."},{"time":561831,"text":"I learned that lesson the hard way\nwhen I was a teenager with my brother."},{"time":566031,"text":"We were driving with friends\ndown a dark road at night,"},{"time":569390,"text":"when a police car stopped us."},{"time":571094,"text":"There had been a robbery in the area\nand they were looking for suspects."},{"time":574681,"text":"The officer approached the car,\nand shined his flashlight on the driver,"},{"time":578839,"text":"then on my brother in the front seat,"},{"time":581285,"text":"and then on me."},{"time":582475,"text":"And his eyes opened wide and he said,"},{"time":585283,"text":"\"Where have I seen your face before?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":587148,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":590075,"text":"And I said,"},{"time":591683,"text":"\"In the front seat.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":593382,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":596405,"text":"But that made no sense to him whatsoever,"},{"time":598549,"text":"so now he thought I was on drugs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":600512,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":602096,"text":"So he drags me out of the car,\nhe searches me,"},{"time":604691,"text":"he marches me over to the police car,"},{"time":606542,"text":"and only when he verified\nI didn't have a police record,"},{"time":610066,"text":"could I show him\nI had a twin in the front seat."},{"time":614417,"text":"But even as we were driving away,"},{"time":616213,"text":"you could see by the look\non his face he was convinced"},{"time":619225,"text":"that I was getting away with something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":621293,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":623293,"text":"Our mind is hard to change\nonce we become convinced."},{"time":626669,"text":"So it might be very natural\nto feel demoralized"},{"time":630133,"text":"and defeated after you fail."},{"time":631844,"text":"But you cannot allow yourself\nto become convinced you can't succeed."},{"time":636242,"text":"You have to fight\nfeelings of helplessness."},{"time":639114,"text":"You have to gain control\nover the situation."},{"time":642393,"text":"And you have to break\nthis kind of negative cycle"},{"time":645009,"text":"before it begins."}]},{"cues":[{"time":646252,"text":"[Stop Emotional Bleeding]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":648191,"text":"Our minds and our feelings --"},{"time":650626,"text":"they're not the trustworthy friends\nwe thought they were."},{"time":653991,"text":"They're more like a really moody friend,"},{"time":656857,"text":"who can be totally supportive one minute,\nand really unpleasant the next."},{"time":662175,"text":"I once worked with this woman\nwho, after 20 years marriage"},{"time":665882,"text":"and an extremely ugly divorce,"},{"time":668311,"text":"was finally ready for her first date."},{"time":670572,"text":"She had met this guy online,"},{"time":672619,"text":"and he seemed nice\nand he seemed successful,"},{"time":675073,"text":"and most importantly,\nhe seemed really into her."},{"time":678629,"text":"So she was very excited,\nshe bought a new dress,"},{"time":681411,"text":"and they met at an upscale\nNew York City bar for a drink."},{"time":685667,"text":"Ten minutes into the date,\nthe man stands up and says,"},{"time":689471,"text":"\"I'm not interested,\" and walks out."},{"time":693798,"text":"Rejection is extremely painful."},{"time":697500,"text":"The woman was so hurt she couldn't move."},{"time":700037,"text":"All she could do was call a friend."},{"time":702198,"text":"Here's what the friend said:\n\"Well, what do you expect?"},{"time":706816,"text":"You have big hips,\nyou have nothing interesting to say."},{"time":710493,"text":"Why would a handsome,\nsuccessful man like that"},{"time":713051,"text":"ever go out with a loser like you?\""},{"time":717092,"text":"Shocking, right, that a friend\ncould be so cruel?"},{"time":720531,"text":"But it would be much less shocking"},{"time":723157,"text":"if I told you it wasn't\nthe friend who said that."},{"time":725957,"text":"It's what the woman said to herself."},{"time":728893,"text":"And that's something we all do,"},{"time":731334,"text":"especially after a rejection."},{"time":733251,"text":"We all start thinking of all our faults\nand all our shortcomings,"},{"time":736720,"text":"what we wish we were,\nwhat we wish we weren't."},{"time":738910,"text":"We call ourselves names."},{"time":740289,"text":"Maybe not as harshly, but we all do it."},{"time":743274,"text":"And it's interesting that we do,"},{"time":744920,"text":"because our self-esteem\nis already hurting."},{"time":748189,"text":"Why would we want to go\nand damage it even further?"},{"time":751236,"text":"We wouldn't make a physical injury\nworse on purpose."},{"time":753882,"text":"You wouldn't get a cut on your arm\nand decide, \"Oh! I know --"},{"time":756808,"text":"I'm going to take a knife and see\nhow much deeper I can make it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":760368,"text":"But we do that with psychological\ninjuries all the time."},{"time":763973,"text":"Why? Because of poor emotional hygiene."},{"time":767442,"text":"Because we don't prioritize\nour psychological health."},{"time":770862,"text":"We know from dozens of studies\nthat when your self-esteem is lower,"},{"time":774446,"text":"you are more vulnerable\nto stress and to anxiety;"},{"time":777931,"text":"that failures and rejections hurt more,"},{"time":780629,"text":"and it takes longer to recover from them."},{"time":783507,"text":"So when you get rejected,\nthe first thing you should be doing"},{"time":786783,"text":"is to revive your self-esteem,"},{"time":788868,"text":"not join Fight Club\nand beat it into a pulp."},{"time":793180,"text":"When you're in emotional pain,"},{"time":795459,"text":"treat yourself with the same compassion"},{"time":798521,"text":"you would expect from a truly good friend."}]},{"cues":[{"time":801361,"text":"[Protect Your Self-Esteem]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":803273,"text":"We have to catch our unhealthy\npsychological habits and change them."},{"time":807598,"text":"And one of unhealthiest and most common\nis called rumination."},{"time":812228,"text":"To ruminate means to chew over."},{"time":814752,"text":"It's when your boss yells at you"},{"time":816965,"text":"or your professor\nmakes you feel stupid in class,"},{"time":819610,"text":"or you have big fight with a friend"},{"time":821883,"text":"and you just can't stop replaying\nthe scene in your head for days,"},{"time":825968,"text":"sometimes for weeks on end."},{"time":828494,"text":"Now, ruminating about upsetting events\nin this way can easily become a habit,"},{"time":833517,"text":"and it's a very costly one,"},{"time":835431,"text":"because by spending so much time focused\non upsetting and negative thoughts,"},{"time":840175,"text":"you are actually putting yourself\nat significant risk"},{"time":843148,"text":"for developing clinical depression,"},{"time":845370,"text":"alcoholism,"},{"time":846660,"text":"eating disorders,"},{"time":847846,"text":"and even cardiovascular disease."}]},{"cues":[{"time":850682,"text":"The problem is,"},{"time":851898,"text":"the urge to ruminate can feel\nreally strong and really important,"},{"time":855863,"text":"so it's a difficult habit to stop."},{"time":858804,"text":"I know this for a fact,"},{"time":860451,"text":"because a little over a year ago,\nI developed the habit myself."},{"time":864540,"text":"You see, my twin brother was diagnosed\nwith stage 3 non-Hodgkin's lymphoma."},{"time":870965,"text":"His cancer was extremely aggressive."},{"time":873133,"text":"He had visible tumors all over his body."},{"time":876904,"text":"And he had to start a harsh course\nof chemotherapy."},{"time":881627,"text":"And I couldn't stop thinking\nabout what he was going through."},{"time":886586,"text":"I couldn't stop thinking\nabout how much he was suffering,"},{"time":890322,"text":"even though he never complained, not once."},{"time":894070,"text":"He had this incredibly positive attitude."},{"time":897021,"text":"His psychological health was amazing."},{"time":900212,"text":"I was physically healthy,\nbut psychologically, I was a mess."},{"time":905303,"text":"But I knew what to do."},{"time":906568,"text":"Studies tell us that even a two-minute\ndistraction is sufficient"},{"time":911243,"text":"to break the urge to ruminate\nin that moment."},{"time":914110,"text":"And so each time I had a worrying,\nupsetting, negative thought,"},{"time":917782,"text":"I forced myself to concentrate\non something else until the urge passed."},{"time":922161,"text":"And within one week,\nmy whole outlook changed"},{"time":926650,"text":"and became more positive and more hopeful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":929509,"text":"[Battle Negative Thinking]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":931267,"text":"Nine weeks after he started chemotherapy,\nmy brother had a CAT scan,"},{"time":936167,"text":"and I was by his side\nwhen he got the results."},{"time":939125,"text":"All the tumors were gone."},{"time":942297,"text":"He still had three more rounds\nof chemotherapy to go,"},{"time":945295,"text":"but we knew he would recover."},{"time":947659,"text":"This picture was taken two weeks ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":953807,"text":"By taking action when you're lonely,"},{"time":956978,"text":"by changing your responses to failure,"},{"time":960225,"text":"by protecting your self-esteem,"},{"time":962645,"text":"by battling negative thinking,"},{"time":964951,"text":"you won't just heal\nyour psychological wounds,"},{"time":968204,"text":"you will build emotional resilience,"},{"time":970787,"text":"you will thrive."},{"time":972664,"text":"A hundred years ago, people began\npracticing personal hygiene,"},{"time":977267,"text":"and life expectancy rates\nrose by over 50 percent"},{"time":981542,"text":"in just a matter of decades."},{"time":983947,"text":"I believe our quality of life\ncould rise just as dramatically"},{"time":988060,"text":"if we all began practicing\nemotional hygiene."}]},{"cues":[{"time":992194,"text":"Can you imagine\nwhat the world would be like"},{"time":994281,"text":"if everyone was psychologically healthier?"},{"time":996841,"text":"If there were less loneliness\nand less depression?"},{"time":1000240,"text":"If people knew how to overcome failure?"},{"time":1003224,"text":"If they felt better about themselves\nand more empowered?"},{"time":1006513,"text":"If they were happier and more fulfilled?"},{"time":1009760,"text":"I can, because that's the world\nI want to live in."},{"time":1014021,"text":"And that's the world\nmy brother wants to live in as well."},{"time":1018371,"text":"And if you just become informed\nand change a few simple habits, well --"},{"time":1024001,"text":"that's the world we can all live in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1027373,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1028563,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}